{"tid":423261,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"調查報告指 IOS 11 耗電速度比 IOS 10 快兩倍","createTime":"2017-10-03T17:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T17:09:35.000Z","uid":142633,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee148bda2b3fb09b881848d74181b68e3c61b17","tid":423261,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:56:19.000Z","msg":"iOS 11 正式推出，無論你是自願或者「接受」蘋果提醒而更新，如果感到電池耗用量突然加快，相信並不是你擁有的 iPhone 或 iPad 的問題。有流動裝置保安機構為 5 萬位用戶進行調查，發現 iOS 11 與 iOS 10 對比之下，前者的平均使用時間只有 96 分鐘，而後者則可用到 240 分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n在近年每次蘋果推出新版本，都有用戶投訴「食電」問題。有時候這個問題可得到解決，例如在幾次充放電之後，電池會重新得到校正，又或者在等候一段時間後，Spotlight 可以完成檔案的優化工作。不過亦有情況是，系統程式或者內置 Apps 的軟件錯誤，令到他們一直耗用你主機的電池。<br />\n<br />\n在 iOS 推出初期，由於有以上提及的因素，用戶報告未必能作準。但在 iOS 11 已經推出一段時間之後，電池校正與檔案優化便不能成為籍口。<br />\n<br />\n據流動裝置保安公司 Wandera 的報告指出，他們對 50,000名 iPhone 與 iPad 的重度用戶進行了調查，對比 iOS 10 與 iOS 11 兩個版本的操作系統，在續航力方面的表現。他們的數據表示，iOS 10 用戶從電量 100％ 用到 0％的時間大約是 240 分鐘，但在 iOS 11 的同類調查裡面，只有 96 分鐘的結果。顯示了最新的 iOS 11 在電池耗用速度方面，比 iOS 10 還要快兩倍。對於舊款 iPhone 以及 iPad 來說，續航力方面的變化來得更明顯。<br />\n<br />\nWandera 稱目前已經將報告交給蘋果，相信用戶需要等待蘋果推出新版 iOS 以解決續航力問題。在本文截稿時最新公開予公眾下載的 iOS 最新版為 11.0.1。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/ios11batterydrain/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2Fios11batterydrain%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=4Ce4bwXm6I27l%2B5pQKYRAr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a3e55839\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/ios11batterydrain/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母部iPhone 6s 倒水咁，兩個鐘內真係無電"},{"pid":"eaecacd4b809041aa7a1d7af2beacb605da4284c","tid":423261,"uid":142633,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"蘋果收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f474b26b978eb023594a44a564aec1e7e3c5f53","tid":423261,"uid":142633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292b3c6cb219fb03f9f211c70b5e2526cdfe41ab","tid":423261,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:09:12.000Z","msg":"我7 plus 未升前都每日返到屋企50%以上<br />\n<br />\n升左11後有日跌到近20%<br />\n<br />\n都係平時咁用 佢既新功能我都無用過"},{"pid":"4d182fe1f5dbfcb8dfaae4847dc19f6ba562894f","tid":423261,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我7 plus 未升前都每日返到屋企50%以上<br />\n<br />\n升左11後有日跌到近20%<br />\n<br />\n都係平時咁用 佢既新功能我都無用過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6s 4個鐘變2個鐘玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a8b459f0dde0604a0b6d889fa3cd04a5b082a","tid":423261,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"ios要去到更新版最後嗰版先叫穩定，樓主又要手痕up上去，up完又屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6c15aecd68a50a3cb875ceb709c15e0b869861","tid":423261,"uid":50588,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:24:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ios要去到更新版最後嗰版先叫穩定，樓主又要手痕up上去，up完又屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIfanboy完全係反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbde4b64681ebf5ed89c3011312c189aa814b09","tid":423261,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ios要去到更新版最後嗰版先叫穩定，樓主又要手痕up上去，up完又屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIfanboy完全係反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><