.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下年9月出ios12又有一大批白老鼠升完屌老母架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d4efcd93b8d0104366ee384e9da0ac3827cb95","tid":423261,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ios要去到更新版最後嗰版先叫穩定，樓主又要手痕up上去，up完又屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n但啲iphone用家唔係成日話apple會將個技術整到完美/成熟先俾用家用咩?</blockquote><br />\n實情係要全體i-user用一年時間幫佢debug，最近仲有幾條友出黎係咁吠有最新做乜唔升最新，又唔明Apple今時不同往日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b9787bd771ea384f1c98c660d9062aab4637f6","tid":423261,"uid":91685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"為升而升，有幾多功能真係有用而又會用到?<br />\n利申: ios7用家"},{"pid":"47b369f35405ba79f1728dd91044dfbfa5d02a42","tid":423261,"uid":14384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"在近年每次蘋果推出新版本，都有用戶投訴「食電」問題。有時候這個問題可得到解決，<span style=\"color: red;\">例如在幾次充放電之後，電池會重新得到校正，又或者在等候一段時間後，Spotlight 可以完成檔案的優化工作。</span>不過亦有情況是，系統程式或者內置 Apps 的軟件錯誤，令到他們一直耗用你主機的電池。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n在 iOS 推出初期，由於有以上提及的因素，用戶報告未必能作準。但在 iOS 11 已經推出<ins>一段時間之後</ins>，電池校正與檔案優化便不能成為籍口。</span><br />\n<br />\n但人地份&quot;報告&quot;，就係9月21日的.  Unwire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wandera.com/blog/ios-11-battery-drain/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wandera.com%2Fblog%2Fios-11-battery-drain%2F&d=4Ce4bwXm6I27l%2B5pQKYRAr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=27b3e249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wandera.com/blog/ios-11-battery-drain/</a>"},{"pid":"7412cd27dd3d29baa84333228bfa2d1ea98791c4","tid":423261,"uid":30857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"推個半成品出黎叫用家更新 好啦聽你講更囉 仆你個街中撚哂伏 又問點解唔等下 我屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"7fab1cddc0f4212d1f6a5a7ef22ed